							<input type="radio" id="storage_list_disable_storage_per_chkb" name="storage_list_disable_storage_chkb" class="w3-radio" value="1" /> &nbsp;<label for="storage_list_disable_storage_per_chkb" class="pointer"><strong><%[ Permanently disable storage ]%></strong> - <%[ disables the storage in Storage resource in the Director configuration (Enabled = no). The storage remains disabled until re-enabled. This method of disabling the storage is resistant to Storage component restarts. ]%></label>
